{"tid":2235919,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Pixar新動畫《Soul》跳過院線 直上Disney+","createTime":"2020-10-09T05:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T05:40:17.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c337e16271ac7a2702e4f26e38f503d2852a376","tid":2235919,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"美國本土戲院重開無期，令聖誕檔期前大家都冇戲好睇，可以話係片方、院線、觀眾「三輸」。但其實仲有一個方法係片方同觀眾唔使輸 (至少唔使輸得咁多)，就係好似Disney咁將《Mulan》直接放上線上平台。而Disney最新宣佈，旗下動畫公司Pixar嘅新戲，都會採用同一策略。<br />\n<br />\nDisney昨日發出公告，指「過去6個月的疫情令市道艱難，但同時亦創造發放內容嘅新方法」，而「第一年就已經有6000萬訂閱者嘅Disney+ 就係讓家庭及Fans們喺屋企收看Pixar最新作品嘅好方法」。同時Disney電影嘅官方Twitter亦發文，確認Pixar新作《Soul》將會於聖誕節當日於Disney+獨家上線，換言之 (至少於美國市場)《Soul》並不會於戲院上映。至於未有Disney+嘅地方 (例如香港)，Disney就話會繼續尋求於戲院上映嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=24933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.menclub.hk%2Fmobile%2Farticle%2Farticle.php%3Fcat%3Dhobby%26aid%3D24933&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr7XxB%2B4AiQz8bo105MOPl14%3D&h=4f3164d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.menclub.hk/mobile/article/article.php?cat=hobby&amp;aid=24933</a>"},{"pid":"3aa174ab820894f3a0e5188586e6bec558e45fd3","tid":2235919,"uid":33668,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"自己直接Soul皮?"},{"pid":"fbba2297c9b58789b717fc93e722981d705fd163","tid":2235919,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3aa174ab820894f3a0e5188586e6bec558e45fd3","tid":2235919,"uid":33668,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"自己直接Soul皮?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f86a01378cef756e9ab73a20c2cfa898522a0b","tid":2235919,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"Mandalorian就出s2 Disney+又Fatfat了"}]}